<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>All-in-One Super App - Pitch by Arsalan</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }
    header {
      background: #2d89e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    section {
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #2d89e5;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .footer {
      background: #2d89e5;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>India’s First All-in-One Super App</h1>
  <p>"One App. Every Service. Every City." <br> By <strong>Arsalan Shaikh</strong></p>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="card">
    <h2>🚫 The Problem</h2>
    <p>Multiple apps for food, grocery, services, and more. Confusing for users, wastes time, and fills phone memory.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>✅ The Solution</h2>
    <p>One single app offering all home services like food delivery, salon, plumber, grocery, and 27+ services across India.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>📊 Market Opportunity</h2>
    <p>80 crore internet users. Huge demand in small cities. No one has built a full combo app yet. First mover advantage!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>💡 Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Customer app: Book & track services</li>
      <li>Vendor app: Register, accept jobs, earn</li>
      <li>Admin dashboard: Control city-wise vendors & orders</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>💰 Business Model</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Commission per order (₹30–100)</li>
      <li>Delivery fees, Vendor subscription</li>
      <li>In-app promotions, ads, and prime users</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🆚 Competitive Edge</h2>
    <p>Swiggy: Food only. Urban Company: Services only. Zepto: Grocery only.  
    <strong>Your app: All in one!</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🚀 Launch Plan</h2>
    <p>Start in Sangamner & Akole. Local marketing. Vendor onboarding. Expand to 10 cities in 6 months.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🧠 Tech Stack</h2>
    <p>Firebase (Auth, DB), Tailwind/HTML, React Native, Razorpay, Google Maps API</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🎯 Vision</h2>
    <p>“Make every small Indian city smarter with one simple app.”<br>
    Helping users save time, and local workers earn more.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>📞 The Ask</h2>
    <p>Looking for ₹5–10 lakh seed investment to build and launch in 5 cities.<br>
    <strong>Contact:</strong> Arsalan Shaikh</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="footer">
  🚀 Let’s Build It. Let’s Scale It. Let’s Rule India.
</div>

</body>
</html>
